45SpeculativeLoad::SpeculativeLoad(Cache& cache, const GlobalFrameID& globalFrameID, const ResourceRequest& request, std::unique_ptr<NetworkCache::Entry> cacheEntryForValidation, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, RevalidationCompletionHandler&& completionHandler)
46 : m_cache(cache)
47 , m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
48 , m_originalRequest(request)
49 , m_bufferedDataForCache(SharedBuffer::create())
50 , m_cacheEntry(WTFMove(cacheEntryForValidation))
51{
52 ASSERT(!m_cacheEntry || m_cacheEntry->needsValidation());
53
54 auto* networkSession = m_cache->networkProcess().networkSession(m_cache->sessionID());
55 if (!networkSession) {
56 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(m_completionHandler)]() mutable {
57 completionHandler(nullptr);
58 });
59 return;
60 }
61
62 NetworkLoadParameters parameters;
63 parameters.webPageProxyID = globalFrameID.webPageProxyID;
64 parameters.webPageID = globalFrameID.webPageID;
65 parameters.webFrameID = globalFrameID.frameID;
66 parameters.storedCredentialsPolicy = StoredCredentialsPolicy::Use;
67 parameters.contentSniffingPolicy = ContentSniffingPolicy::DoNotSniffContent;
68 parameters.contentEncodingSniffingPolicy = ContentEncodingSniffingPolicy::Sniff;
69 parameters.request = m_originalRequest;
70 parameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain = isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain;
71 m_networkLoad = makeUnique<NetworkLoad>(*this, nullptr, WTFMove(parameters), *networkSession);
72 m_networkLoad->startWithScheduling();
73}

89void SpeculativeLoad::willSendRedirectedRequest(ResourceRequest&& request, ResourceRequest&& redirectRequest, ResourceResponse&& redirectResponse)
90{
91 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "Speculative redirect %s -> %s", request.url().string().utf8().data(), redirectRequest.url().string().utf8().data());
92
93 std::optional<Seconds> maxAgeCap;
94#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
95 if (auto* networkStorageSession = m_cache->networkProcess().storageSession(m_cache->sessionID()))
96 maxAgeCap = networkStorageSession->maxAgeCacheCap(request);
97#endif
98 m_cacheEntry = m_cache->storeRedirect(request, redirectResponse, redirectRequest, maxAgeCap);
99 // Create a synthetic cache entry if we can't store.
100 if (!m_cacheEntry)
101 m_cacheEntry = m_cache->makeRedirectEntry(request, redirectResponse, redirectRequest);
102
103 // Don't follow the redirect. The redirect target will be registered for speculative load when it is loaded.
104 didComplete();
105}

107void SpeculativeLoad::didReceiveResponse(ResourceResponse&& receivedResponse, ResponseCompletionHandler&& completionHandler)
108{
109 m_response = receivedResponse;
110
111 if (m_response.isMultipart())
112 m_bufferedDataForCache = nullptr;
113
114 bool validationSucceeded = m_response.httpStatusCode() == 304; // 304 Not Modified
115 if (validationSucceeded && m_cacheEntry)
116 m_cacheEntry = m_cache->update(m_originalRequest, *m_cacheEntry, m_response);
117 else
118 m_cacheEntry = nullptr;
119
120 completionHandler(PolicyAction::Use);
121}

123void SpeculativeLoad::didReceiveBuffer(Ref<SharedBuffer>&& buffer, int reportedEncodedDataLength)
124{
125 ASSERT(!m_cacheEntry);
126
127 if (m_bufferedDataForCache) {
128 // Prevent memory growth in case of streaming data.
129 const size_t maximumCacheBufferSize = 10 * 1024 * 1024;
130 if (m_bufferedDataForCache->size() + buffer->size() <= maximumCacheBufferSize)
131 m_bufferedDataForCache->append(buffer.get());
132 else
133 m_bufferedDataForCache = nullptr;
134 }

137void SpeculativeLoad::didFinishLoading(const WebCore::NetworkLoadMetrics&)
138{
139 if (m_didComplete)
140 return;
141 if (!m_cacheEntry && m_bufferedDataForCache) {
142 m_cacheEntry = m_cache->store(m_originalRequest, m_response, m_bufferedDataForCache.copyRef(), [](auto& mappedBody) { });
143 // Create a synthetic cache entry if we can't store.
144 if (!m_cacheEntry && isStatusCodeCacheableByDefault(m_response.httpStatusCode()))
145 m_cacheEntry = m_cache->makeEntry(m_originalRequest, m_response, WTFMove(m_bufferedDataForCache));
146 }
147
148 didComplete();
149}

160void SpeculativeLoad::didComplete()
161{
162 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
163
164 if (m_didComplete)
165 return;
166 m_didComplete = true;
167 m_networkLoad = nullptr;
168
169 // Make sure speculatively revalidated resources do not get validated by the NetworkResourceLoader again.
170 if (m_cacheEntry)
171 m_cacheEntry->setNeedsValidation(false);
172
173 m_completionHandler(WTFMove(m_cacheEntry));
174}

178static void dumpHTTPHeadersDiff(const HTTPHeaderMap& headersA, const HTTPHeaderMap& headersB)
179{
180 auto aEnd = headersA.end();
181 for (auto it = headersA.begin(); it != aEnd; ++it) {
182 String valueB = headersB.get(it->key);

184 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "* '%s' HTTP header is only in first request (value: %s)", it->key.utf8().data(), it->value.utf8().data());

186 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "* '%s' HTTP header differs in both requests: %s != %s", it->key.utf8().data(), it->value.utf8().data(), valueB.utf8().data());
187 }
188 auto bEnd = headersB.end();
189 for (auto it = headersB.begin(); it != bEnd; ++it) {
190 if (!headersA.contains(it->key))
191 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "* '%s' HTTP header is only in second request (value: %s)", it->key.utf8().data(), it->value.utf8().data());
192 }

197bool requestsHeadersMatch(const ResourceRequest& speculativeValidationRequest, const ResourceRequest& actualRequest)
198{
199 ASSERT(!actualRequest.isConditional());
200 ResourceRequest speculativeRequest = speculativeValidationRequest;
201 speculativeRequest.makeUnconditional();
202
203 if (speculativeRequest.httpHeaderFields() != actualRequest.httpHeaderFields()) {
204 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "Cannot reuse speculatively validated entry because HTTP headers used for validation do not match");
205#if !LOG_DISABLED
206 dumpHTTPHeadersDiff(speculativeRequest.httpHeaderFields(), actualRequest.httpHeaderFields());
207#endif
208 return false;
209 }
210 return true;
211}
